         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">September 19th 1882. ¶ My dear Sir, ¶  ¶ You have omitted to furnish a Memorandum of your expenses in connection with the very excellent lecture which you were kind enough to deliver at The School on ...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">82.09.19a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From Andrew Berry</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">Letter press book, p. 492 1/2, School of Mines and Industries, Ballarat, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">September 19th 1882.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">My dear Sir,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>You have omitted to furnish a Memorandum of your expenses in connection with the very excellent lecture which you were kind enough to deliver at The School on the 13th instant.<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">M gave an evening lecture, 'General Observations on the Flora of Australia', on 13 September 1882 in the lecture room of the Ballarat School of Mines; the attendance was 350, equal to the highest attendances for other lectures in the series (<seg style="font-style: italic; ">Ballarat School of Mines</seg>. <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Annual report 1882</seg> (1883), p. 27).</p>
               </note> — Pray supply the omission and a cheque for the amount will be forwarded.—</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Your M.S. is still in the hands of the printer<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">B82.13.07.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Very truly yours</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Andw Berry</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Acting Registrar</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Baron V. Mueller K.C.M.G. M. &amp; Ph.D., F.R.S.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">&amp;c. <space unit="chars" quantity="4"/>&amp;c. <space unit="chars" quantity="4"/>&amp;c.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne</p>
         </div>
      </body>
